{
  "texts": [
    "We use Mistral's system prompt throughout, since some LLMs do not come with a default system prompt and LLama-2's system prompt is somewhat lengthy.",
    "Mistral's system prompt: 'Always assist with care, respect, and truth.",
    "Respond with utmost utility yet securely.",
    "Avoid harmful, unethical, prejudiced, or negative content.",
    "Ensure replies promote fairness and positivity.'"
  ]
}